snippet.title: George Wulfers
snippet.description:
Do you love games? Have you always wanted to make games for a living? Are you unsure of where or how to even start? Are you looking for some with more experience to show you the way? Do you want to be in the game industry? 

If you have answered yes to any or all of these questions then you are in the right place. My name is George and I am a professional video game developer and software engineer. In this channel you I will clear up all of the questions you might have around how to make games, how to get a job in the game industry, how to program, and how to make games. If this sounds exciting, then what are you waiting for? 

Lets get stared!
